list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: added sendResetPasswordEmail function on Android channel + added support for full StitchUser details

task.summary: added support for a collection's functions "count" , "findOne", "find", "deleteOne" , but without filtering on iOS Channel
added starting support for collection function "updateOne", "updateMany", with filtering on Android Channel + added most of the Update Operators
added support for collection function "watch" on Android Channel
fixed little bugs in android channel
added "or", "and" logical querying operators + make more modular code
added starting support for collection function "watchWithFilter"
cleaned code + added Namespace getter for a collection
added support for calling a Stitch function on Android channel
Added support for using projection and limit a collection find function results on Android channel
Added support for using sort on a collection find function results on Android channel
added support for authentication using Google/Facebook on Android Channel
added Google/Facebook configuration for example app
mocked fixed for using google_sign_in plugin
using id-part only for auth code instead full string
added support for collection function "aggregate" on Android Channel
fixed bug on android channel of mismatch type when using request time on Cloud Function
added sendResetPasswordEmail function on Android channel + added support for full StitchUser details
fixed collection watch functions + null exception on filter function
added AuthListener in order to listen to auth state changes in the app
